	* session.h (struct systemtap_session): Added kprobes_text
	variables - kprobes_text_initialized, kprobes_text_start, and
	kprobes_text_end.
	* elaborate.cxx (systemtap_session::systemtap_session):
	kprobes_text variables get initialized.

